  <div class="main-body"><a class="section_anchor" id="wb_1" name="wb_1"></a><h1>Welcome to Cocoda.<br />
Export sales, marketing and consultancy for specialist confectionery.</h1>
<p>Established in 2004 after 10 years in the sector, Cocoda is focused on two key activities:</p>
<h2>Export Sales Management</h2>
<p>Cocoda is the world&rsquo;s leading exporter of Great British premium confectionery, contracted to manage the Export sales of carefully selected complementary premium confectionery brands.<br />
<br />
Many of the brands Cocoda manages have received Gold at the prestigious &lsquo;Great Taste Awards&rsquo;, widely acknowledged as the &lsquo;Food Oscars&rsquo;, recognising exceptional product quality and integrity. <br />
<br />
Click through the brands section to learn more about the brands Cocoda manages. In addition, Cocoda has access to a variety of other quality confectionery items, so if you are looking for something not shown on the brand pages, please contact Cocoda with your requirements.</p>
<h2>Sales and Marketing Consultancy</h2>
<p>With extensive sales and marketing experience in the sector, Cocoda also undertakes consultancy for brand owners, manufacturers, distributors and retailers in the confectionery sector. Click on &lsquo;Consultancy&rsquo; to find out more about these services.</p></div>
